The Indian swash-buckler skipper recently shared his team's official video on social media in which he along with his highly entertaining team mates like AB de Villiers , Chris Gayle and Shane Watson could be seen grooving to the beats of RCB's official song.
The RCB stars could be seen shaking their legs on a dance number involving renowned DJ Nikhil Chinappa and Mr Nags.
Excited RCB players started sharing the funny video on their Twitter handles.
Kohli and Gayle were seen dancing to the tunes of Shane Watson, who played an awesome number on his guitar.